    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely zero road rash, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium hand-stitched leather upholstery retains its original suppleness and scent, with no visible wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist sensors, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a high shine, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life of gentle use and preventative care. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
